8
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,800
Nature's strategy isn’t random!

9
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,600
Ultimately, the method depends on the environment.

10
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:36,000
Each strategy has its pros and cons, perfectly timed for survival.

